accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: Microfilm is open for research. Brittle or damaged items are available at the discretion of RAC.

originalsloc.head: Existence and Location of Originals
originalsloc.p: Original paper collection is available at the American Philosophical Society.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The collection includes correspondence, diaries, drafts of articles, and speeches. The papers relect the history of medical science in the first half of the 20th century.
The original paper collection is available at the American Philosophical Society.

bioghist.head: Biographical / Historical
bioghist.p: Simon Flexner (1863-1946) was a physician, administrator, professor of pathology at the University of Pennsylvania, and director of the Rockefeller Institute for Medical Research (1901-1935).
